com.github.dandelion.datatables.core.callback
Class Callback

java.lang.Object
  com.github.dandelion.datatables.core.callback.Callback

public class Callback
extends Object

Callback called by DataTables.

A callback is composed of:

  • a CallbackType available among all callbacks proposed by DataTables
  • a JavascriptFunction that is executed in the callback

Since:
0.8.9
